<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA60">
<l>mēlāya mēkaṅkaḷ kūṭiyōr poṉvilaṅkal</l>
<l>pōlā moḷiputaittā lovvātē - mālāya</l>
<l>kaimmā matakkaḷiṟṟuk kārurivai pōrttapō</l>
<l>tammāṉ ṟirumēṉi yaṉṟu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It was not equal to when the clouds that are above gather [and] bury the light</l>
<l>that is like a golden mountain, that day, the sacred body of the lord</l>
<l>at the time he covers [it] with the black hide of the great rutting elephant bull</l>
<l>with a trunk that was dark/big.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
